This is liburbi-cpp, a C++ library for URBI.
It provides an API to connect to an URBI server, send messages
(both "-Aà la printf" and "à la iostream") ,  register callback -b
functions that will be called when messages with a given tag 
is received.

See the doc/ folder for the Documentation: it contains a quick
HTML tutorial and the Doxygen-generated reference.

Many examples are included to get you started in the src/examples
directory.
